headline: TMUS Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates on Solid Demand for Postpaid Services
summary: TMUS tops Q4 estimates as revenues climb to $24.33B on robust postpaid demand, adding 2.4M net customers and lifting EBITDA and cash flow.
